Privacy Policy for SASL App
Effective Date: [2025-11-05]
South Asia Securities Ltd. (“we”, “our”, “us”) operates the SASL App (the “App”) to provide clients with access to portfolio details, market updates, and reports related to the Dhaka Stock Exchange (DSE).
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our App.
________________________________________
1. Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of information:
•	Account Information: Client ID, name, contact details, and account number (for authentication purposes).
•	Usage Data: Basic analytics such as device type, version, and app usage frequency.
•	Financial Data: Information related to your holdings, portfolio, and trade reports retrieved securely from South Asia Securities’ back-office system.
We do not collect unnecessary personal information or access your phone contacts, photos, or location.
________________________________________
2. How We Use Your Information
We use the information to:
•	Display portfolio and market data related to your account.
•	Provide requested services such as viewing reports and summaries.
•	Improve app performance and client experience.
•	Communicate important updates or notifications.
________________________________________
3. Data Security
We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information against unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.
All communication between the App and our servers is encrypted (HTTPS/TLS).
________________________________________
4. Data Sharing
We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties.
Information is used only within South Asia Securities Ltd. for providing services to clients.
________________________________________
5. Your Rights
You may:
•	Request access or correction of your personal information.
•	Request deletion of your data (subject to regulatory requirements).
To exercise these rights, please contact us at: southasiasecuritiesapp@gmail.com

